HEADWORD: Jadish
<hw>Jad"ish</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Vicious; ill-tempered;
resembling a jade; -- applied to a horse.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Unchaste; -- applied to a woman.</def>
<rj><au>L'Estrange.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

